column5: Any advice on which branch of I-35 to take through the Twin Cities?
35e thru St. Paul. South there is construction and creates bottlenecks
Best option 34W What time a day will you be passing through? 6:30 - 9:00 am and 2:30 to 6:30 pm = a bad time to visit our lovely area. Unless were talking Saturday or Sunday
We should hit the south end of the metro area around 2:00 on Friday afternoon.
Best to hit 35E through St Paul.
